Generate a bash script to prepare the specified resource.

Usage:
  kwm script [cluster-admin pki startup]
  kwm script [controlplane-node etcd-node worker-node] <nodeKey>

Examples:
  # Inspect script to generate public key infrastructure.
  kwm script pki

  # Run script to generate public key infrastructure.
  kwm script pki | bash

  # Save script to generate public key infrastructure (to share with others).
  kwm script pki > generate-pki
